We have just tested 3.4-3.6 mongodb, according to this. https://github.com/SkyAPMTest/agent-integration-test-report#mongodb

I think the driver lib updates. 

@rainleon we are welcome you to contribute fix to support high versions

# Global Topology Query
```graphQL
{
  getGlobalTopology(duration:{step:MINUTE, start: "2019-05-13 2100", end: "2019-05-13 2130"}){
    nodes{
      id
      type
      isReal
      name
    },
    calls{
      id
      detectPoints
      source
      target
      sourceComponents
      targetComponents
    }
  }
}
```

